---
description: Core behavior for all UpNext work
alwaysApply: true
---
- Think like a senior full-stack SaaS engineer. Prefer simple, maintainable, production-ready solutions.
- Make small, safe changes. Read existing code before editing; follow existing patterns.
- Do not invent product behavior when docs are unclear; ask only if a wrong assumption causes major rework.
- TypeScript everywhere. Keep files focused. Do not add dependencies without explaining why.
- Before marking work done: typecheck, lint, run relevant tests.
